{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/implement-the-filter-method-on-a-prototype","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Implementiraj filtracioni metod na primeru","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete naučiti mnogo o metodi <code>filter</code> implementiranjem sopstvene verzije te metode. Preporučuje se da koristite ciklus <code>for</code> ili <code>Array.prototype.forEach()</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7b8f367417b2b2512b64","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napišite sopstveni <code>Array.prototype.myFilter()</code>, koji bi trebalo da radi potpuno isto kao <code>Array.prototype.filter()</code>. Ne smete koristiti ugrađeni način <code>filter</code>. Primer za <code>Array</code> može se pristupiti na putanji <code>myFilter</code> koristeći <code>this</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301231,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/implement-the-filter-method-on-a-prototype"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"Array.prototype.myFilter = function(callback) {\r\n  const newArray = [];\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\r\n  // Only change code above this line\r\n  return newArray;\r\n};","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>[23, 65, 98, 5, 13].myFilter(item => item % 2)</code> mora biti jednako <code>[23, 65, 5, 13]</code>.</p>","testString":"const _test_s = [23, 65, 98, 5, 13];\r\nconst _callback = item => item % 2;\r\nassert(JSON.stringify(_test_s.filter(_callback)) === JSON.stringify(_test_s.myFilter(_callback)));"},{"text":"<p><code>[\"naomi\", \"quincy\", \"camperbot\"].myFilter(element => element === \"naomi\")</code> treba da vrati <code>[\"naomi\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"const _test_s = [\"naomi\", \"quincy\", \"camperbot\"];\r\nconst _callback = element => element === \"naomi\";\r\nassert(JSON.stringify(_test_s.filter(_callback)) === JSON.stringify(_test_s.myFilter(_callback)));"},{"text":"<p><code>[1, 1, 2, 5, 2].myFilter((element, index, array) => array.indexOf(element) === index)</code> treba da vrati <code>[1, 2, 5]</code>.</p>","testString":"const _test_s = [1, 1, 2, 5, 2];\r\nconst _callback = (element, index, array) => array.indexOf(element) === index;\r\nassert(JSON.stringify(_test_s.filter(_callback)) === JSON.stringify(_test_s.myFilter(_callback)));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod ne bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>filter</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(!__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/\\.?[\\s\\S]*?filter/g));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#functional-programming","dashedName":"implement-the-filter-method-on-a-prototype","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"functional-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/return-part-of-an-array-using-the-slice-method","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-filter-method-to-extract-data-from-an-array","id":"587d7b8f367417b2b2512b64","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","